<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Error Rates>
We are investigating increased error rates and latencies for the AWS Management Console in the EU-WEST-3 Region

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased Error Rates>
Between 2:13 PM and 3:08 PM PDT we experienced increased error rates and latencies for the AWS Management Console in the EU-WEST-3 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
